parameters:
"Hey everyone, good morning. It's great to see you all so
energetic today."

"Of course we're energetic, we get to see Lady Makoto every
day♡ Good morning to you too, Mamoru-kun. Looks like you
didn't oversleep today!"

"Yesterday, you barely made it on time with Lady Makoto!
Really, you should practice going to bed and waking up
early!"

"If Mamoru-kun oversleeps, then Lady Makoto, who waits for
you every morning, might be late too!"

"You should act with the awareness of being Lady Makoto's
fiancé!"

"F-fiancé!? We're dating, but we're not at that stage
yet..."

"What! Was it all just a game to you!? I thought our
relationship was with the intention of marriage!"

"N-no, of course it's not a game! But we're still students,
you know? Marriage is too soon!"

"...Hehehe, I'm just kidding! Mamoru, you're so fun to
tease. But I do hope to be your bride in the future♡"

"Of course! I'll definitely marry you! I promise to make you
happy! Absolutely!"

"Grrr!! Flirting with Lady Makoto right in front of us～! I'm
going crazy with jealousy! I feel like I'm going to lose
it!"

"I'm so envious! So envious! I want to flirt like this from
the morning too!"

"I want to be in love too～! I wish for a gentleman who will
be devoted to me wholeheartedly～!"
"I want to be in a wonderful couple like you two～!"

That day, the incident at the factory quickly became known
among Makoto's fans, especially the part where I stood up to
protect Makoto and almost got hit. The fans started to
respect me because of it.

Thanks to that, our relationship was smoothly accepted, and
now, as you can see, I've become friendly with the
followers. Makoto prioritizes our time together, and I'm
truly happy.
